><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:11:12.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂 娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"Merry Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}